expression = re.compile('[' + rfc._SEPARATOR_CHARS + ']')
separators = ['(', ')', '<', '>', '@', ',', ';', ':', '\\', '"', '/', '[',
    ']', '?', '=', '{', '}', ' ', '\t']
for separator in separators:
    self.assertTrue(bool(expression.fullmatch(separator)), msg=
        "Separator '{s}' was not found".format(s=separator))
